packageResponses.name: The Ghan Alice Springs to Darwin with Charles Darwin Sunset Dinner Cruise
packageResponses.description:
Following an early evening departure from Alice Springs enjoy a regionally inspired dinner as the train journeys north. Morning breaks as you awake in the tropical north and you are served a hearty breakfast in preparation for exploring Katherine with a choice of a number of Off Train Experiences that take in the awesome natural beauty of the area. Back onboard, share your experiences with new and old friends as the train makes its way through lush, green tropics and eventually arrives in Darwin by early evening. Transfer to your accommodation (as booked by you) and enjoy the following day at leisure. Cap off your trip to remember by joining Darwin Harbour Cruises and lap up a sunset you're unlikely to forget. 
Please Note: Accommodation is not included

packageResponses.name: The Ghan Expedition Darwin to Adelaide
packageResponses.description: To intimately experience the very best the heart of our nation has to offer, the four-day three-night Ghan Expedition truly is a journey beyond. In addition to exploring Katherine on your first day of this all-inclusive adventure, there is a full day of touring Alice Springs that concludes with dinner under the stars, plus another full day exploring the truly unique underground mining town of Coober Pedy. Wake-up on your final day to a view of the Flinders Ranges outside your window and then it's on to Adelaide.

packageResponses.name: The Ghan Adelaide to Alice Springs
packageResponses.description: A leisurely midday departure is complimented with a gourmet lunch being served soon after we pull away from the Adelaide Parklands Terminal. Journey through the picturesque Clare Valley and Mid-North and pass by some of the oldest rock formations on the planet via the Flinders Ranges. Following your first night onboard you can alight the train to watch a breathtakingly beautiful sunrise over the desert. Your all-inclusive journey continues north to the Red Centre while you enjoy regionally inspired dining onboard as you glide through the MacDonnell Ranges and into Alice Springs.

packageResponses.name: The Ghan Adelaide to Darwin with Charles Darwin Sunset Dinner Cruise
packageResponses.description:
Setting off from Adelaide, you'll travel coast to coast through the fiery Red Centre, experiencing Australia at its dramatic best on this all-inclusive journey. After your first night onboard take in an outback sunrise in Marla before the train makes its way to Alice Springs where a half a day of Off Train Experiences await. Your third and final day includes more extraordinary experinces in Katherine before arriving into Darwin as early evening falls. Transfer to your accommodation (as booked by you) and enjoy the following day at leisure. Cap off your trip to remember by joining Darwin Harbour Cruises and lap up a sunset you're unlikely to forget. 
Please Note: Accommodation is not included
